291 template <class Element, int Dimensions>
292 inline int TArray<Element, Dimensions>::GetElementIndex(const IndexType& index) const
293 {
294  int elementIndex = 0;
295  int cumulatedSizes = 1;
296  for (int i = 0; i < Dimensions; ++i){
297  Q_ASSERT(index[i] >= 0);
298  Q_ASSERT(index[i] < m_sizes[i]);
299 
300  elementIndex += index[i] * cumulatedSizes;
301 
302  cumulatedSizes *= m_sizes[i];
303  }
304 
305  return elementIndex;
306 }
